data.description: Looking for a wonderful county property with 15.2 acres of land (or buy additional 6.8 ac) and an all brick 4br home with walk out basement? Here is your opportunity to own a well built home on your own private wooded property as you sit and watch the deer and turkey roam, this long inviting front porch enters you into the foyer where a formal dining room is on your right, straight ahead into the great room you can see to the back deck area, the kitchen has a large breakfast bar and breakfast eat in area, split bedroom arrangement with two guests and a full bath on your left and the large primary suite with sitting area, primary bath with double vanities, whirlpool tub, and separate 4 ft shower, huge walk in closet are on the opposite side for privacy, the laundry, additional pantry space, and basement stairs and double garage also occupy this area. The walk out basement has a steel beam/concrete frame, it has the additional living space den, 4th bedroom, full bath, and an island kitchen approx 1175 sf. of living space and would make a nice teen/mother in law suite with all the space and layout. Propane leased, gas heat, stove and gas logs. ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY PROVIDED TO BUYER!
